Time to challenge myself!

18
00:03:22,244 --> 00:03:23,120
Here I go!

19
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:26,415
Revving up for idea burn!

20
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:32,170
Hello, Eudial speaking...

21
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:40,929
It's me. About our next
target. Why don't we go
after an athlete?

22
00:03:40,929 --> 00:03:42,097
All right...

23
00:03:42,097 --> 00:03:43,849
I've found one.

24
00:03:44,433 --> 00:03:45,559
Very good.

25
00:03:45,559 --> 00:03:51,231
I have the perfect Daimon
to accompany you!

26
00:03:51,356 --> 00:03:55,485
[nasty laugh]

27
00:03:55,485 --> 00:04:01,867
[coughing] Note to self:
don't run and cackle...

28
00:04:08,623 --> 00:04:11,877
Hurdle!

29
00:04:45,577 --> 00:04:47,078
Wow! What a large
gymnasium...

30
00:04:47,078 --> 00:04:49,539
If I'm lucky enough
to get accepted here

