next year. I'll play
volleyball in there.

32
00:04:51,958 --> 00:04:54,628
Don't worry. I'm sure
you'll get in.

33
00:04:54,628 --> 00:04:57,380
You guys have been studying
really hard lately.

34
00:04:57,380 --> 00:04:58,298
Mm‐hm.

35
00:04:58,298 --> 00:05:00,592
I meant Minako and Mako...

36
00:05:00,592 --> 00:05:02,219
Rei...

37
00:05:02,219 --> 00:05:04,721
What? I'm kind of hurt
by what you said. And

38
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:06,932
the look you gave me
wasn't nice, either.

39
00:05:06,932 --> 00:05:09,017
Oh. Really? Yes, really.
In fact, I'm

